column2: SELECT   p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.survey FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.zWarning = # AND s.class = &&& AND s.survey = &&&  AND p.petroMag_r < # AND ra > # AND ra < #  AND dec > # AND dec < #
